text: Teodora Dimoska (; born 29 September 2000) is a Macedonian footballer who plays as a forward for 1. liga club ŽFK Tiverija Istatov and the North Macedonia women's national team. ==References== Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Macedonian women's footballers Category:North Macedonia women's international footballers
